# RBAC × Cedar (embedded) — application-registry permissions (endpoints/pages/components)
# Requires: make up + make seed. IDs below come from the deterministic dataset (seed 42);
# regenerate examples from bench/tuples/rbac.json after reseeding with a different seed.

@host = http://localhost:8080

### ALLOW — persona holds a role that grants "render" on this component
POST {{host}}/v1/authorize
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "engine": "cedar",
  "model": "rbac",
  "principal": "psn-000449",
  "action": "render",
  "resource_type": "Component",
  "resource": "cmp/hr/attendance-board/daily-grid"
}

### DENY — same persona, no role grants "render" on this other component
POST {{host}}/v1/authorize
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "engine": "cedar",
  "model": "rbac",
  "principal": "psn-000449",
  "action": "render",
  "resource_type": "Component",
  "resource": "cmp/hr/payroll-run/adjustment-editor"
}

### Playground — endpoint execute (edit freely; see catalog/services.json for IDs)
POST {{host}}/v1/authorize
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "engine": "cedar",
  "model": "rbac",
  "principal": "psn-000449",
  "action": "execute",
  "resource_type": "Endpoint",
  "resource": "ep/finance/invoice-approve"
}
